r of local Hessian computations. For all these\nmetrics, the proposed approach shows superior performance against state-of-the\nart techniques like GIANT and FedNL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 17:52:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 21:38:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
