15$ years before gradually dissipating. The process repeats\nevery $34$ years and reproduces all trends in Pleione's variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 20:59:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
