se injections tests indicate that rather\nhigh signal-to-noise ratio (S/N>250) is required to correct for the observed\nactivity signal on HD128621.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 21:02:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
